            %h3 Who we are
            %p.paragraph-margin Welcome to Edit Salon set in Aston cum Aughton, Sheffield. Edit is a boutique contemporary salon specialising in hair and beauty and is part of the Aveda flagship. It's a space to relax and unwind and be pampered. Our expert team are trained with Aveda to the highest level to create bespoke colours especially for you. Our focus is creating a style that is adaptable for each individuals homelife as well as making their experience an unforgettable one!

