                  %strong Salon Founder & Creative Director
                %p.small-text Abby has 10years experience in the hair industry and is immensely passionate about training. Abby has trained at Vidal Sassoon academy in London and has frequently attended London Fashion week. She states; 'Training is extremely important to me for keeping up to date with the latest trends, if you don't keep training you get left behind! That's the beauty of this industry, you are always learning.'
            %li.team-list__item
