                %p.small-text Becky has been in the industry for 6 years as a hairstylist. She is naturally outgoing helping to put her guests at ease. She believes that listening to her guests is key when trying to achieve their desired look. Taking time to give a thorough consultation before she starts creating something amazing!
            %li.team-list__item
