                %p.small-text Lois has 10 years in the hairdressing industry and has come to join us from across the Pennines. She has done session work with Kevin Murphy and trained to a high standard with Aveda. Being a blonde bombshell herself it is also her signature, she loves blondes! She prides herself in being professional and making her guests feel at home.
